To estimate carrier trap state density in the MAPbI3 films with and without PEA, we performed space-charge-limited current (SCLC) measurements on hole-only and electron-only devices (Fig. S9, Supporting Information). The trap state densities are calculated from Eq. (4) [54]:4Nt=2VTFLε0εrqL2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
